      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic, reliable vehicle! It is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and comfortable driving experience. While it shows a few minor signs of its previous adventures, it remains a clean, dependable, and high-quality choice for anyone looking for a great ride at a fair price!",
