    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory shine with absolutely no scratches, dents, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Every feature and electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a history of meticulous maintenance and care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in like-new condition.",
